<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 14:30:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Tether 收购软银在比特币财务公司的股份</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/tether-buys-out-softbank-stake-in-bitcoin-treasury-firm</link><description>Tether 收购了软银集团 (SoftBank Group Inc.) 在数字资产财务公司 Twenty One Capital Inc. 中的所有权，在寻求将该公司与另外两家企业合并之际，增强了其对比特币累加器的控制权。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iz7uK6q5yZnk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 12:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/tether-buys-out-softbank-stake-in-bitcoin-treasury-firm</guid></item><item><title>新加坡因“严重违规”而撤销 Bsquared 加密货币许可证</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/singapore-revokes-bsquared-crypto-permit-over-serious-breaches</link><description>新加坡中央银行吊销了当地加密货币流动性提供商的主要支付机构许可证，这对于监管机构来说是罕见的举动，因为这个城市国家寻求减轻该行业的风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i3oeJKADLOwU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 10:36:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-20/singapore-revokes-bsquared-crypto-permit-over-serious-breaches</guid></item><item><title>100 亿美元的数字银行挤兑后 DeFi 储户仍然失踪</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-19/defi-depositors-remain-missing-after-10-billion-digital-bank-run</link><description>三个月期国库券的收益率正在上升。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iM8qEzC3cMDI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-05-19/defi-depositors-remain-missing-after-10-billion-digital-bank-run</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 深化推动允许押注热门初创企业的价值</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-19/polymarket-deepens-private-companies-push-with-data-partnership</link><description>Polymarket 计划使用纳斯达克私募市场的数据，在散户投资者的狂热兴趣中寻求扩大对非上市公司的押注。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i6GoKk.ztiao/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 15:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-19/polymarket-deepens-private-companies-push-with-data-partnership</guid></item><item><title>FTX 前高管推出“无损失”人工智能交易平台</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-19/former-ftx-executive-launches-a-no-loss-ai-trading-platform</link><description>在失败的加密货币交易所 FTX 的欧洲分公司，帕特里克·格鲁恩 (Patrick Gruhn) 目睹交易员多次因高风险押注而亏损。现在，他正在推出一款产品，即使是在零资本的情况下，最精明的投资者也可以从中获利。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRc_.C4wW93o/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-19/former-ftx-executive-launches-a-no-loss-ai-trading-platform</guid></item><item><title>加密货币犯罪随着绑架、诈骗和人为胁迫而升级</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-19/crypto-conferences-up-security-after-attacks-scams</link><description>经过一年的针对加密货币持有者的绑架、袭击和武装入室盗窃事件后，该行业正在竞相加强防御。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifixhJSfZcUg/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-19/crypto-conferences-up-security-after-attacks-scams</guid></item><item><title>加密货币清算额突破 8 亿美元，比特币跌至两周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-18/bitcoin-btc-hits-two-week-low-as-crypto-liquidations-top-half-a-billion</link><description>由于中东动荡导致需求回落，促使交易员削减头寸，比特币跌至两周多来的最低水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFO3RVBfktrg/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 02:56:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-18/bitcoin-btc-hits-two-week-low-as-crypto-liquidations-top-half-a-billion</guid></item></channel></rss>